The request for
[ConnectionService.CreateConnection][google.cloud.bigquery.connection.v1.ConnectionService.CreateConnection].

Attributes:
    parent (str):
        Required. Parent resource name. Must be in the format
        ``projects/{project_id}/locations/{location_id}``
    connection_id (str):
        Optional. Connection id that should be
        assigned to the created connection.
    connection (google.cloud.bigquery_connection_v1.types.Connection):
        Required. Connection to create.

parent.description: Required. Parent resource name. Must be in the format ``projects/{project_id}/locations/{location_id}``

connection_id.description: Optional. Connection id that should be assigned to the created connection.
Output only. The unique identifier of the SIP Trunk connection.

state.description: Output only. State of the connection.

update_time.description: Output only. When the connection status changed.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_update_time``.

error_details.description: Output only. The error details for the connection. Only populated when authentication errors occur.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_error_details``.

certificate_state.description: Output only. The status of the certificate authentication.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_certificate_state``.

error_message.description: The error message provided from SIP trunking auth service  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``_error_message``.
